= English =

Now i primarily GNU Emacs user. I had used XEmacs few years ago.

My translation of GNU Emacs tutorial & refcard are now included into GNU Emacs 22, but you can take it from my Emacs page

I have number of articles about using Emacs for performing different tasks. You can find them [http://xtalk.msk.su/~ott/en/emacs/index.html here (in English)] and [http://xtalk.msk.su/~ott/ru/emacs/index.html here (in Russian)]

I also write about my works with Emacs in [http://alexott.blogspot.com my blog] 

= Russian =

Я в основном использую GNU Emacs, хотя использовал и XEmacs несколько лет назад.

[http://xtalk.msk.su/~ott/ru/emacs/index.html Раздел про Emacs] моей домашней страницы.  Я также пишу про Емакс и другие свои работы в своем  [http://alexott-ru.blogspot.com блоге]

